Tyler.Long.Turo on Instagram 

Thanks for checking out my profile!

   As a Power Host here on the Turo platform a trip with me comes with some guarantees! I always respect everyone’s business and will assure you that I offer 5 Star customer service with professional communication as well as a detailed/reliable car for your trip!

   A quick background of myself, I am from Las Vegas, NV and have lived up and down the west coast! In addition to Turo I am also a Firefighter/EMT and enjoy doing that very much.  I have an extreme passion for cars which  ultimately lead me here to Turo which I am so thankful to be apart of.  My wife and I began hosting with our first car in February 2021 and haven’t stopped since! We try and keep a revolving fleet of new vehicles so whether you are renting for work/business or for your weekend vacation you can do so in style!

   I have personally used Turo on countless occasions including my wedding where I rented a brand new Ford Bronco! Having used Turo myself I know how valuable being a reliable/trustworthy host is. 

  All of our rentals are one hundred percent contactless for both pickup and drop off. The entire process is very streamline and takes hardly anytime at all. Simply show up to the address listed on your reservation, follow the “check in” procedure on Turo, take your pre trip photos and be on your way! For “checkout” you will follow the Turo prompts on the app, take post trip photos, make sure the key is in the car, lock it from the app then on your way! More detailed instructions will be provided upon booking but that is the overall picture when you rent with me!

   I hope to earn your business and share our awesome fleet of cars with you, if you should have any questions and are on Instagram feel free to write me a message on there!
Tyler.Long.Turo

   Take care everyone and safe travels!

Hello! I'm Nina, and I'm delighted to be your go-to host on Turo.

As part of a family-owned business, we're passionate about cars and exceptional service. We have a diverse range of vehicles that are meticulously maintained and ready to meet your needs. Whether you're seeking to conquer obstacles in our robust 2021 Silverado 2500 High Country, cruise in style in our 2017 Corvette Z06, or embark on a long trip with our comfortable and spacious 2017 Suburban Premier, we've got you covered.

Perhaps you'd like to drive around town in a sleek, blacked-out limo-like vehicle? We can arrange that too. If you prefer something economical yet sophisticated, our 2020 and 2021 Camrys, 2021 Malibu, 2020 and 2021 Corollas, 2019 Avalon, and 2021 Audi A4 are great choices. And for those who enjoy the blend of comfort and agility, we offer the 2021 and 2022 Camaros and the 2021 Blazer. We've recently added the versatile 2023 Tiguan to our lineup for those who appreciate compact yet powerful SUVs.

When you rent from us, we handle all the checking-in processes for our vehicles, ensuring they are in the best condition and ready to hit the road when you are. Our aim is to make your car rental experience as easy and enjoyable as possible.

Being a family business, we bring a personal touch to everything we do. We're dedicated to going the extra mile to ensure your rental experience is exceptional.

Thank you for choosing us as your Turo host. I'm looking forward to assisting you and ensuring your rental experience exceeds your expectations.

Happy driving!

To some of us, a car is not just something that gets us from point A to point B. Cars, driving, the whole experience is something I'm passionate about. We spend so much time in our cars, and I believe we should enjoy the experience. 

I treat Turo like a business. I strive for convenience, quick drop offs, and cleanliness. Let me know if there's anything I can do to improve your trip!

With a lifelong passion for cars, games, and sports, I bring a diverse blend of experiences to the world of car sharing. As a former professional gamer in StarCraft: Brood War and Counter-Strike, my skills in communication and teamwork now fuel my commitment to providing an exceptional car sharing experience.

Outside of gaming and cars, my life is brightened by the presence of Bella, my delightful half Labrador, half Golden Retriever companion. Although Bella is a major part of my life, I ensure she never accompanies me in any of my Turo vehicles to maintain the highest standards of cleanliness.

Having originated from a strong customer service background and currently immersed in the gaming industry, I began hosting on Turo in September 2023. This role has been a joyful extension of my career, allowing me to meet wonderful new people and deliver first-rate service with every interaction. My goal is to enhance your experience and make every trip memorable.

Whether you’re planning a road trip, need a car for commuting, or simply want to explore the great sights of California, consider me your go-to for a fun and seamless adventure in the vibrant San Francisco Bay Area!

In my fleet, every vehicle isn’t just a rental; it's a car I would personally drive. This philosophy ensures that each car meets a high standard of quality and reliability. I take no shortcuts when it comes to maintenance and service—all work is carried out at authorized dealerships or by a trusted mechanic to guarantee that everything is up to par. I do this not just to meet expectations, but to exceed them, ensuring that all my vehicles are safe, reliable, and ready to enhance your journey. When you choose one of my cars, you're not just renting a vehicle—you're gaining peace of mind for your travels.
